{
  "stem": "2373.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only, it was known that that is the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Listen to the wireless, to the news.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never got it back, and I never asked for it back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When it came?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the-- the last three weeks, we lived in that ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then from there on the 13th of June, we were-- everybody, not only from Levice, the Jewish people, but from all over the vicinity from the little villages-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] we went to the railway station with little parcels, whatever we were allowed to take.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think 50 kilos or something like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were put in cattle wagons and off.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were-- they were [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1,500 people.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1,500 people.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And from that, only hundred came back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It took-- it took us three days, three horrible days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the cattle wagon was-- was sealed from the outside.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no window, no door, nothing, nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were there about-- it wasn't hardly place to sit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because if we wanted to sit, somebody has to stand.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] changing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was sitting for half and hour, somebody else was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was crammed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and it was inhuman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was one bucket in the corner for our bodily functions in front of everybody.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, it was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, only when we arrived somewhere in three-- three day's time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know if it's day or night, because it was dark there all the time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't even know that we left Hungary, only when we arrived and the door was-- the wagon was unsealed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we had arrived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there we saw men in striped uniforms and striped caps.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
